% Facts
can_fly(sparrow).
can_fly(pigeon).
can_fly(parrot).
cannot_fly(penguin).
cannot_fly(ostrich).

% Rules
bird_can_fly(Bird) :- can_fly(Bird).
bird_can_fly(Bird) :- cannot_fly(Bird), write(Bird), write(' cannot fly'), nl, fail.

output:
?- bird_can_fly(sparrow).
true.

?- bird_can_fly(penguin).
penguin cannot fly
false.
